snippet.title: Tactical Manager gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Tactical Manager, Dos PC game produced by Talking Birds in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/tactical-manager/1819/
Tactical Manager it's a football management game, setting you in charge of one of the teams in the top 2 English divisions of the time and giving you control over transfers, tactics and training regimes as you aim to guide your team to success.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
The Manager - https://youtu.be/Qt-iLvf80_U
Ultimate Soccer Manager - https://youtu.be/eehPhJKCpO0
International Sensible Soccer - https://youtu.be/XkGDcx__x6c
